rows.label: fev06_140_107_msg0001
rows.name: Right...let's head for Goth Isut Port!

rows.label: fev06_140_107_msg0002
rows.name:
How about we take our
time and stroll there?

rows.label: fev06_140_107_msg0004
rows.name:
It's been ages since
I last went back home to Luxuria,
ya know?

rows.label: fev06_140_107_msg0005
rows.name:
I've been taken care of here for
a long time, so I want to indulge
in the memories a bit.

rows.label: fev06_140_107_msg0007
rows.name: I know, right? Surprising, isn't it?

rows.label: fev06_140_107_msg0009
rows.name:
Are you bringing back lots of souvenirs
for everyone you haven't seen in a while?

rows.label: fev06_140_107_msg0010
rows.name:
Nah, don't need 'em!
My old man wouldn't want
that stuff anyway.

rows.label: fev06_140_107_msg0011
rows.name: Now, let's walk to Goht Isut Port.

rows.label: fev06_140_107_msg0012
rows.name: You could grab some Odifa on the way!

rows.label: fev06_140_107_msg0013
rows.name:
They don't have it in Luxuria,
so it's your last chance, ya know?

rows.label: fev06_140_107_msg0014
rows.name: I told you to shut up!
